  "title": "Service Desk Analyst (Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>Our esteem client is looking for Assistant Engineers to join their 24/7 Service Desk to provide high availability of enterprise IT services.</p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Act as the Single point of contact to users, stakeholders and third party vendors.</li><li>Monitoring enterprise networks and server systems and maintaining documentation and records.</li><li>Ensure escalation of incidents to appropriate vendors.</li><li>Resolve and track incidents/service requests and ensure closure within agreed SLA.</li></ul><p></p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum Higher NITEC in Information Technology with 1 to 2 years of relevant working experience.</li><li>Excellent customer service skillsand communication skills</li><li>Prior experience in Network Operations Centre (NOC) environment.</li><li>Work location – Near Cashew MRT station</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br />We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p><p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : kelvin<a href=\"mailto:jeline@starcareerconsulting.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><br />Kelvin (Reg. No. R1872625)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
